flavorText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "B9BFC9A94BA60EF7E0AD04BA1A95BFA4", "Caravans are being intercepted while traveling East of the Halcyon gates. The most likely culprits are the Forsaken Blade, a disciplined group of bandits who have taken over the Citadel of the Steel Bloom. While the real Steel Bloom Knights are considered ancient history, a new order arises among the desperate and angry hillfolk, and it\'s worth investigating what their motivations are against the Kaelar Empire. None of them are likely to be virtuous or sensible. Fighting back will require subverting their efforts to impede the Kaelar people, such as taking down their traps, wearing down their numbers, and stealing back the supplies they owe.")
mainObjectiveText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "47137F81452E80D628FCD4A5B74CE736", "Become an enemy of the Forsaken Blade")
calloutDescription: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "FCDF57B745ED24C853510A8201F27EAD", "A group of guards in Kaelar uniform stand at the bridge. They keep searching down the road East for a caravan that isn\'t arriving.")
